Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}偶然の虚飾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:59.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}喰い合いを急ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:05.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}死んだ眼の獣よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Never be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}感情何度込めても
