Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:21.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Believe in my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:24.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}純粋で美麗な勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}さあルーレット止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:30.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}非情に選ぶがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:57.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}判定はただ敢え無く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:04.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}敗者は消え　勝者には　Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:08.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}次が待っている
