Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}一度捨てた命に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:27.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}足掻いてはいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now take this. My life
